targets.queryText:
SELECT
    sellers.name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT books.id) AS total_books,
    COUNT(DISTINCT electronics.id) AS total_electronics,
    COUNT(DISTINCT dvds.id) AS total_dvds
FROM
    sellers
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_books_links ON sellers.id = sellers_books_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    books ON sellers_books_links.book_id = books.id
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_electronics_links ON sellers.id = sellers_electronics_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    electronics ON sellers_electronics_links.electronic_id = electronics.id
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_dvds_links ON sellers.id = sellers_dvds_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    dvds ON sellers_dvds_links.dvd_id = dvds.id
GROUP BY
    sellers.id, sellers.name;
targets.rawQueryText:
SELECT

    COUNT(DISTINCT electronics.id) AS total_electronics,
    COUNT(DISTINCT dvds.id) AS total_dvds
FROM

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN

GROUP BY
    sellers.id, sellers.name;

targets.queryText:
SELECT
    sellers.name AS seller_name,
    AVG(COALESCE(books.price, electronics.price, dvds.price)) AS average_price
FROM
    sellers
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_books_links ON sellers.id = sellers_books_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    books ON sellers_books_links.book_id = books.id
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_electronics_links ON sellers.id = sellers_electronics_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    electronics ON sellers_electronics_links.electronic_id = electronics.id
LEFT JOIN
    sellers_dvds_links ON sellers.id = sellers_dvds_links.seller_id
LEFT JOIN
    dvds ON sellers_dvds_links.dvd_id = dvds.id
GROUP BY
    sellers.id, seller_name;

targets.queryText:
SELECT
    electronics.brand AS brand_name,
    COUNT(electronics.id) AS total_electronics
FROM
    electronics
GROUP BY
    electronics.brand
ORDER BY
    total_electronics DESC;
